{
  "category": "combat",
  "templates": [
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_001",
      "text": "Abyssal Lord has a knockback. Position against the wall or you'll get punted into the Nipper King's room.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Abyssal Lake"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_002",
      "text": "Don't stand in the fire at Fallen Braxonia. Those floor patches tick hard and the Braxonian Honor Guards will chain-pull you back in.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "warning", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fallen Braxonia"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_003",
      "text": "Careful pulling in Ripper's Keep. The Sivakayan Raiders and Sivakayan Reavers are linked. You pull one, you get three.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Ripper's Keep"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_004",
      "text": "Arcanists should kite the Loomingwood Minotaur Soldiers. They hit like carts but they're slow. Keep your distance and nuke.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Loomingwood"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_005",
      "text": "Bring a Druid for heals in Prielian Cascade. Savannah Priel hits the whole group and you need sustained healing to survive.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "group", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Prielian Cascade"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_006",
      "text": "Magic resist is mandatory for Jaws of Sivakaya. Vessel Siraethe will melt anyone without at least ten percent MR.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "resist", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Jaws of Sivakaya"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_007",
      "text": "Let the Paladin build aggro before you DPS. I've watched too many Windblades get one-shot opening on Fallen Fernalla.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "aggro", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Blooming Sepulcher"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_008",
      "text": "You're too low for The Blight. Come back at twenty-eight at least, or the Doomwalkers will flatten you before you zone in properly.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "warning", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_009",
      "text": "Kill the Sivakayan Cleric first. Always. If you let it heal the pack, you'll never burn them down.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "aggro"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Blacksalt Strand", "Rottenfoot", "Ripper's Keep"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_010",
      "text": "Diamond Colossus telegraphs its slam. When it raises both arms, move. Melee need to step out and re-engage after the hit lands.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rockshade Hold"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_011",
      "text": "Stormcallers, save your mana for the boss pulls in Vitheo's Rest. The trash before Nazura the Traitor is long. Pace yourselves.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Vitheo's Rest"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_012",
      "text": "Demented Malaroth is no joke. That thing hits harder than most dungeon bosses. Do not engage solo.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Malaroth's Nesting Grounds"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.1
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_013",
      "text": "Fire and earth resist help enormously in Rockshade Hold. The Pyroclast does pure fire damage. Gear accordingly.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "resist", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rockshade Hold"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_014",
      "text": "Overseer Orlok calls adds in Old Krakengard. Burn him fast or the Molorai Archmages will overwhelm your healer.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Old Krakengard"],
      "personality_affinity": ["aggressive"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_015",
      "text": "The Spark Queen in Lost Cellar does chain lightning. Spread out. If you stack, one bolt hits everyone.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Lost Cellar"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_016",
      "text": "Reaver tanks, pop your defensive stance before engaging Harbinger of Corruption. Its opening hit is brutal.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "boss"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_017",
      "text": "Blight Wyrm is end-of-zone hard. You want a full group, resist gear, and a Druid who knows the fight.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_018",
      "text": "In the Elderstone Mines, the Slumbering Queen summons Fungal Drones. Kill the adds immediately or they stack up fast.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Elderstone Mines"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_019",
      "text": "Aggro the A Faerie Drone first in Faerie's Brake. Those casters will nuke your cloth wearers from range if left alone.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "aggro"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Faerie's Brake"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_020",
      "text": "Gruhglor in Fernalla's Revival Plains drops Woebringer. Worth farming. But bring friends -- he's tougher than he looks.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fernalla's Revival Plains"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 0.9
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_021",
      "text": "The Molorai Militia in Vitheo's Watch attack on sight. Don't assume all humanoids are friendly. I learned that the hard way.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "warning", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Vitheo's Watch"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_022",
      "text": "Interrupt the Molorai Archmage casts in Old Krakengard. Their nukes will wreck your group if they get them off.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Old Krakengard"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.1
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_023",
      "text": "Astra, Rogue of the Stars is the best boss to farm at endgame. Six best-in-slot weapons off one mob. Bring your A-team.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Soluna's Landing"],
      "personality_affinity": ["aggressive"],
      "relationship_min": 3.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_024",
      "text": "Void resist on everyone for Apparition of Vitheo. That fight in Vitheo's Rest is pure magic damage.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "resist", "boss"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Vitheo's Rest"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_025",
      "text": "You need to say Shadowtide to Styria Olafur before entering Vitheo's Rest. Skip that and the Aquilamar will aggro you.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "warning", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Vitheo's Rest"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_026",
      "text": "The Grassland Ogre Shamans in Underspine Hollow heal. Mark them and burn them first, or the pull never ends.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "aggro"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Underspine Hollow"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_027",
      "text": "Druo the Reborn always spawns in Underspine Hollow. The other four bosses rotate. Don't count on seeing Agsha of the Soil every run.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Underspine Hollow"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_028",
      "text": "Windblades, do not open with your burst on Prince Oslind. Let the tank establish. That boss turns on a dime.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "aggro", "boss"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fallen Braxonia"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_029",
      "text": "Nipper King summons Nipper Pups throughout the fight. Have your Stormcaller handle the adds while melee stay on the boss.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Abyssal Lake"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_030",
      "text": "Sivakayan Prioresses in Blacksalt Strand do dark rituals. Interrupt or stun them. If the cast goes off, your healer can't keep up.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Blacksalt Strand"],
      "personality_affinity": ["aggressive"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_031",
      "text": "Monarch of the Flame in Braxonian Desert hits like a truck. Stack fire resist and bring two healers if your group is undergeared.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "resist"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Braxonian Desert"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_032",
      "text": "Pull single Dire Wolves in Silkengrass Meadowlands. If you body-pull a second one, the damage doubles and your healer falls behind.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "tactics", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Silkengrass Meadowlands"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 0.9
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_033",
      "text": "Sableheart, Steed of Sivakaya charges the farthest target. Casters, stay close to the tank or you'll eat the charge.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Jaws of Sivakaya"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.1
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_034",
      "text": "Don't pull the Tamed Malaroth packs in Prielian Cascade without CC. Each one hits like a boss on its own.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "warning", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Prielian Cascade"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_035",
      "text": "Druids, save your big heal for the Volcanic Giant's eruption phase. It's a party-wide spike and you need to top everyone fast.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rockshade Hold"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_036",
      "text": "Raval, The First Paladin in Soluna's Landing drops Erandian Avenger. Best shield in the game. Worth the grind.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Soluna's Landing"],
      "personality_affinity": ["aggressive"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_037",
      "text": "Balthom, Soldier of Sivakaya resists physical damage heavily. Bring casters for that fight or it takes forever.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "resist"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Jaws of Sivakaya"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_038",
      "text": "Swamp Wyrm in Rottenfoot has a poison aura. Melee need poison resist or you'll tick down fast between heals.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "resist"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rottenfoot"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_039",
      "text": "You're under-level for Azynthi's Garden. That zone starts at thirty. The Molorai Anointed will eat you alive.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "warning", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Azynthi's Garden"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_040",
      "text": "Eldoth Molorai himself is the final fight on the island. Full group, full resist gear, no shortcuts. Wipe and you run back from the ferry.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Azynthi's Garden"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.1
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_041",
      "text": "Hypnic in the third Mysterious Portal is endgame-level. Do not underestimate that fight just because it's a portal zone.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Mysterious Portal"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_042",
      "text": "When fighting Addison Priel, burn the Priel Swiftblades first. They enrage if Addison drops below half while they're still up.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Prielian Cascade"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_043",
      "text": "Ghost of Wyland Sercher in Island Tomb is the first real group test. Spread when he channels. Stack when he melees. Simple.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Island Tomb"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_044",
      "text": "Darkwarden Ilyth in Vitheo's Rest under the lighthouse is the hardest single boss in the game. Do not go in cocky.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "warning"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Vitheo's Rest"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_045",
      "text": "Ravager, The First Infected in Elderstone Mines is where Sivakaya's corruption first took root. Fight is nasty -- bring antidotes.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Elderstone Mines"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_046",
      "text": "The Blight has no safe camps. Every direction is aggressive mobs. If you're low on health, gate out. Don't try to run.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "warning", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": ["cautious"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_047",
      "text": "Paladin tanks, use your taunt rotation on Stoneman Colossus. It drops aggro periodically and will pivot to your casters.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "aggro", "boss"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rockshade Hold"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_048",
      "text": "Lazalith, Soldier of Sivakaya in Blacksalt Strand drops Voidbloom Ring. Great for tanks. But he's tougher than the wildlife around him.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Blacksalt Strand"],
      "personality_affinity": ["helpful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 0.9
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_049",
      "text": "Dusken Giant hits slow but devastates. Melee, keep moving between swings. Ranged can free-cast the entire fight if positioned right.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Duskenlight Coast"],
      "personality_affinity": ["tactical"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "combat_tac_050",
      "text": "Secluded Sanctuary throws all four shadows at you at once. Shadow of Brax, Shadow of Soluna, Shadow of Vitheo, Shadow of Fernalla. You need a kill order or you wipe.",
      "context_tags": ["combat", "boss", "group", "tactics"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Secluded Sanctuary"],
      "personality_affinity": ["commanding"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.2
    }
  ]
}
